# Global shortcuts

**Rule hierarchy:** `workflow.mdc` detects session phrases and delegates here for backup/deploy/db shortcuts. Deploy tier details live in `deploy-safety-hostinger.mdc`. Local recovery is in `local-runtime-recovery.mdc`.

## Backup ritual

| Operator says | Agent action |
|---------------|--------------|
| **`backup project`**, **`create backup`**, **`backup`** | Interactive ritual — **AskQuestion** buttons each step ([CURSOR.md](../custom-scriptz/backup-system/CURSOR.md), [interactive-workflows.mdc](./interactive-workflows.mdc)) |
| **`backup quick`**, **`backup project quick`** | **Non-interactive:** run `npm run msc:backup:quick` from repo root — no questions, no note prompt |
| **`backup full`**, **`backup project full`** | **Non-interactive:** run `npm run msc:backup:quick:full` from repo root — no questions, no note prompt |
| **`clean backups`**, **`purge old backups`** | Run `npm run msc:backup:clean` (deletes backups older than the 10 most recent) |
| **`clean zips`**, **`purge deploy zips`** | Run `npm run backup:clean-zips` (keeps 3 newest in `zips/`) |

Quick commands use default backup root (`G:\Cursor_Project_BackUpz\MyStudioChannel`), auto-suggest next `msc-website-v2-*` folder, and `--yes`.

After quick backup completes, report destination path and `.cursor/BackUp-Notez.md`.

